Interface QueryModel

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Criteria
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AssociationQuery, DefaultQuery, RawQuery

    public interface QueryModel
extends Criteria
    Main interface for constructing queries at either compilation or runtime.

    1.0
